bring up a phrase which expresses our compassion so that the one that's normally used is may your sufferings lesson may all your sufferings come to an end so that would come out of the visudimaga this um compendium of buddhism written by buddhagosa in the middle ages or you can make up some other phrase that makes that makes sense to you but just for this it might be good just to stay with this one here

